rating_comment:
The place was nightmare for my partner. The water was dirty and my partner became sick.
The room was full of mold. Bedsheet was dirty.
The wasroom was full of soil and crack. Snails, Silverfish and worms were crawling around the washroom. Toilet flash is broken so floating poo will be there . No cloth hanger. No rack.
The place is quiet and natural. Location is good.
The host is gentle and soft-spoken but alluring.
The host also offers access to Banani club.
I wouldn't recommend this place. This place is full of health hazard. I left the place and moved to a good rated 3 star hotel which was only 1.4 times more expensive than this Airbnb but enjoyed full of mental peace.
